### Get all products
GET http://localhost:8000/api/products

### Get products by category
GET http://localhost:8000/api/products?categoryId=1

### Get single product
GET http://localhost:8000/api/products/1

### Create product (admin)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/products
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Premium Headphones",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "price": 199.99,
  "discountPrice": 179.99,
  "stockLeft": 50,
  "badge": "Bestseller",
  "description": "High-quality wireless headphones with noise cancellation"
}

### Update product (admin)
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 189.99,
  "stockLeft": 45
}

### Delete product (admin)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Add product media (admin)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/products/media
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "mediaUrl": "https://example.com/images/headphones.jpg",
  "mediaType": "image"
}

### Remove product media (admin)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/products/media/1/product/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN